  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A single center, observational, prospective study to improve knowledge about non-invasive
      ventilation, obtaining data about compliance, efficacy, imaging in patients who already
      receive non-invasive ventilation as standard of care.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
