  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Number of patients requiring NIV in a large university hospital. Incidence of NIV failure (including patient compliance) and NIV related complications. Imaging (chest ultrasound) in a subgroup of patients before and after receiving NIV.</measure>
    <time_frame>Outcome measures will be assessed every day and participants will be followed for the duration of hospital stay, an expected average of 1 weeks.</time_frame>
  </primary_outcome>
